## Employee Table

```sql
CREATE TABLE Employee (
    emp_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    emp_name VARCHAR(50),
    salary DECIMAL(10,2),
    hire_date DATE,
    department_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (department_id)
