# Question 2: Department Wise Employee Count

## SQL Query

```sql
SELECT d.department_name,
       COUNT(e.emp_id) AS employee_count
FROM Department d
JOIN Employee e
ON d.department_id = e.department_id
GROUP BY d.department_name;
```

