# Question 4: Employees Whose Salary Is Greater Than Department Average

## SQL Query

```sql
SELECT e.*
FROM Employee e
WHERE e.salary >
(
    SELECT AVG(salary)
    FROM Employee
    WHERE department_id = e.department_id
);
```

