# Question 9: Find Duplicate Records

## SQL Query

```sql
SELECT emp_id,
       emp_name,
       salary,
       department_id,
       COUNT(*) AS duplicate_count
FROM Employee_Duplicate
GROUP BY emp_id,
         emp_name,
         salary,
         department_id
HAVING COUNT(*) > 1;
```

